  checks for 82 Lua files; `luarocks lint dwarfspec-0.1.0-1.rockspec` and
  `git diff --check` pass.
- DFHack's embedded Lua 5.3 parsed and executed the complete 19-test
  product-independent live suite, including ordinary widget, overlay widget,
  and complete screen classes and existing instances. Fluent editing,
  clicking, input, inspection, dynamic selection, implicit tree capture, and
  stale-subject diagnostics pass without passing raw targets to normal
